MYERS, PHILIP E.; Aboveground Storage Tanks. Mc Graw Hill. ISBN 0-07-044272-X. 2006 Bibliografía
NEWMAN, DONALD G et al. Engineering economic analysis (9th Ed). ISBN13: 978-0-19-516807-5. 2004
QUEROL, ENRIQUE. www.ptdu.org.es
